'''布蘭登·艾克'''（{{lang-en|'''Brendan Eich'''}}，{{bd|1961年|7月4日|||catIdx=Eich, Brendan}}）<ref name="NYT_1997_09_09">{{cite news|url=http://www.nytimes.com/1996/09/09/business/part-artist-part-hacker-and-full-time-programmer.html|title=Part Artist, Part Hacker And Full-Time Programmer|first=Steve|last=Lohr|date=1996-09-09|work=The New York Times|accessdate=2015-03-29|archive-date=2015-05-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150526162851/http://www.nytimes.com/1996/09/09/business/part-artist-part-hacker-and-full-time-programmer.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，美國程式技术专家與企業家，[[JavaScript|JavaScript]]主要創造者與架構師，曾任[[Mozilla公司|Mozilla公司]]的[[技術長|技術長]]，並曾短暫擔任[[執行長|執行長]]<ref>{{cite web|last=Swisher|first=Kara|title=Mozilla Co-Founder Brendan Eich Resigns as CEO, Leaves Foundation Board|url=http://recode.net/2014/04/03/mozilla-co-founder-brendan-eich-resigns-as-ceo-and-also-from-foundation-board|publisher=Recode|accessdate=April 3, 2014|archive-date=2015-03-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150330093353/http://recode.net/2014/04/03/mozilla-co-founder-brendan-eich-resigns-as-ceo-and-also-from-foundation-board/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 生平 ==
布蘭登·艾克生於[[美國|美國]][[加州|加州]]的[[森尼韦尔_(加利福尼亚州)|森尼維爾市]]，在[[聖塔克拉拉大學|聖塔克拉拉大學]]（Santa Clara University）就讀時，最初主修[[物理學|物理學]]，大三時因興趣轉變转投[[計算機科學|計算機科學]]領域，後取得[[數學|數學]]與[[計算機科學|計算機科學]][[學士|學士]]學位。1986年取得[[伊利諾伊大學香檳分校|伊利諾伊大學香檳分校]]計算機科學[[碩士|碩士]]學位<ref name="NYT_1997_09_09"/>。

畢業後進入[[視算科技|SGI]]工作，在此工作七年，主要負責[[作業系統|作業系統]]與網路功能<ref name="aboutcom">{{Citation|contribution-url=http://inventors.about.com/library/inventors/bl_javascript.htm|contribution=Brendan Eich and JavaScript|title=Inventors|publisher=About|accessdate=2016-08-12|archive-date=2012-12-08|archive-url=https://archive.today/20121208142259/http://inventors.about.com/od/jstartinventions/a/JavaScript.htm|dead-url=no}}.</ref>。之後他在MicroUnity工作了三年<ref name="aboutcom"/>。1995年4月，任職於[[網景|網景]]期間，為[[網景瀏覽器|網景瀏覽器]]開發出[[JavaScript|JavaScript]]，之後成為[[网页瀏覽器|网页瀏覽器]]领域應用最廣泛的[[腳本語言|腳本語言]]之一<ref name="Saternos2014">{{cite book|last=Saternos|first=Casimir|title=Client-Server Web Apps with JavaScript and Java|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=3b40AwAAQBAJ&pg=PT32|accessdate=4 April 2014|date=2014-03-28|publisher=O'Reilly Media|isbn=9781449369293|pages=32–|archive-date=2015-03-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150315025005/http://books.google.com/books?id=3b40AwAAQBAJ&pg=PT32|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Severance">{{cite news|url=http://www.computer.org/csdl/mags/co/2012/02/mco2012020007.pdf|title=JavaScript: Designing a Language in 10 Days|last=Severance|first=Charles|date=February 2012|work=Computer (magazine)|accessdate=April 4, 2014|archive-date=2016-03-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305202500/http://www.computer.org/csdl/mags/co/2012/02/mco2012020007.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>。1998年，艾克協助成立Mozilla.org，2003年在[[美國線上|美國線上]]決定結束網景部門營運後，艾克協助成立了[[Mozilla基金会|Mozilla基金会]]<ref name="Seibel2009">{{cite book|last=Seibel|first=Peter|title=Coders at Work: Reflections on the Craft of Programming|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=nneBa6-mWfgC&pg=PA132|accessdate=4 April 2014|date=2009-09-16|publisher=Apress|isbn=9781430219484|pages=132–|archive-date=2015-03-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150315024821/http://books.google.com/books?id=nneBa6-mWfgC&pg=PA132|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2014年3月24日，艾克晉升為[[Mozilla公司|Mozilla公司]]執行長引發[[同性戀|同性戀]]族群抗议，歸咎於艾克2008年曾捐助1000美元-{zh-hans:支持; zh-tw:支持}-[[加利福尼亞州8號提案|加利福尼亞州8號提案]]<ref>{{cite news|first=Deborah|last=Netburn|title=Brendan Eich's Prop. 8 contribution gets Twittersphere buzzing|publisher=[[LA_Times|LA Times]]|date=2012-04-04|url=http://www.latimes.com/business/technology/la-fi-tn-brendan-eich-prop-8-contribution-20120404,0,6341761.story|accessdate=2012-04-17|archive-date=2012-04-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120407222147/http://www.latimes.com/business/technology/la-fi-tn-brendan-eich-prop-8-contribution-20120404,0,6341761.story|dead-url=no}}</ref>。此事引發線上交友網站OkCupid抵制使用Firefox瀏覽器<ref>{{Cite news|url = http://www.independent.co.uk/life-style/gadgets-and-tech/news/online-dating-site-okcupid-calls-for-firefox-boycott-to-protest-at-antigay-marriage-boss-9226904.html|title = OkCupid calls for Firefox boycott to protest anti-gay marriage CEO Brendan Eich|last = Johnston|first = Ian|date = April 1, 2014|work = Independent|accessdate = June 5, 2014|archive-date = 2014-08-11|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140811214813/http://www.independent.co.uk/life-style/gadgets-and-tech/news/online-dating-site-okcupid-calls-for-firefox-boycott-to-protest-at-antigay-marriage-boss-9226904.html|dead-url = no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url = http://www.advocate.com/business/technology/2014/03/26/mozilla-ceo-responds-antigay-allegations|title = OkCupid calls for Firefox boycott to protest anti-gay marriage CEO Brendan Eich|last = Byrdum|first = Sunnivie|date = March 26, 2014|work = The Advocate|accessdate = |archive-date = 2014-10-31|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20141031193950/http://www.advocate.com/business/technology/2014/03/26/mozilla-ceo-responds-antigay-allegations|dead-url = no}}</ref>，一些Mozilla員工亦要求辭職<ref>{{cite web|url=http://arstechnica.com/business/2014/03/mozilla-employees-to-brendan-eich-step-down|title=Mozilla employees tell Brendan Eich he needs to "step down"|work=Ars Technica|date=March 27, 2014|accessdate=March 28, 2014|first=Sam|last=Machkovech|archive-date=2014-03-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140328215554/http://arstechnica.com/business/2014/03/mozilla-employees-to-brendan-eich-step-down/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://subfictional.com/2014/03/24/on-brendan-eich-as-ceo-of-mozilla|title=On Brendan Eich as CEO of Mozilla|work=Subfictional Studios|date=March 24, 2014|accessdate=April 7, 2014|first=Christie|last=Koehler|archive-date=2015-03-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150328074947/http://subfictional.com/2014/03/24/on-brendan-eich-as-ceo-of-mozilla/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。Mozilla董事會成員希望他留在公司中扮演不同的角色<ref name=":0">{{Cite news|url = https://www.theregister.co.uk/Print/2014/04/08/mozilla_anti_gay_marriage_boycott/|title = Gay marriage foes outraged at Mozilla CEO flap, call for boycott|last = McAllister|first = Neil|date = April 8, 2014|work = The Register|accessdate = June 5, 2014|archive-date = 2017-10-01|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20171001122649/https://www.theregister.co.uk/Print/2014/04/08/mozilla_anti_gay_marriage_boycott/|dead-url = no}}</ref>。

2014年4月3日，艾克宣佈從Mozilla離職。艾克在他的個人部落格中寫道：“Mozilla的使命遠超過我們任何一人，無法勝任Mozilla的領導職位”<ref name=Kim1>{{cite news|last=Kim|first=Susana|title=Mozilla CEO Brendan Eich Resigns After Protests from Gay Marriage Supporters|url=http://abcnews.go.com/Business/mozilla-ceo-resigns-calif-gay-marriage-ban-campaign/story?id=23181711|accessdate=April 3, 2014|newspaper=ABC News|date=April 3, 2014|archive-date=2014-07-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140713082813/http://abcnews.go.com/Business/mozilla-ceo-resigns-calif-gay-marriage-ban-campaign/story?id=23181711|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="eichblog">{{Cite web|title=Brendan Eich steps down as Mozilla CEO|date=April 3, 2014|url=https://blog.mozilla.org/blog/2014/04/03/brendan-eich-steps-down-as-mozilla-ceo|publisher=blog.mozilla.org|accessdate=April 8, 2014|archive-date=2020-02-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200220052759/https://blog.mozilla.org/blog/2014/04/03/brendan-eich-steps-down-as-mozilla-ceo/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。美國作家{{link-en|安德魯·沙利文|Andrew Sullivan}}在談到艾克的離職時說“沒有一絲證據表明他曾經在Mozilla中歧視過一個同性戀者”<ref>{{cite web|url=http://dish.andrewsullivan.com/2014/04/04/dissents-of-the-day-63/|title=Dissents Of The Day|work=The Dish|accessdate=2017-11-04|archive-date=2017-08-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170824035630/http://dish.andrewsullivan.com/2014/04/04/dissents-of-the-day-63/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，而艾克被迫離職一事“應該讓那些對[[包容|包容]]和[[多元化|多元化]]社會感興趣的人感到厭惡”<ref>{{cite web|url=http://dish.andrewsullivan.com/2014/04/03/the-hounding-of-brendan-eich/|title=The Hounding Of A Heretic|work=The Dish|accessdate=2017-11-04|archive-date=2017-11-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171107083013/http://dish.andrewsullivan.com/2014/04/03/the-hounding-of-brendan-eich/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.mediaite.com/tv/andrew-sullivan-blows-colberts-mind-with-defense-of-brendan-eich/|title=Andrew Sullivan Blows Colbert’s Mind with Defense of Brendan Eich|date=10 April 2014|work=mediaite.com|accessdate=2017-11-04|archive-date=2017-06-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170603140243/http://www.mediaite.com/tv/andrew-sullivan-blows-colberts-mind-with-defense-of-brendan-eich/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.techtimes.com/articles/5432/20140412/andrew-sullivan-sparks-ire-of-gay-community-over-defense-of-former-mozilla-ceo-brendan-eich.htm|title=Andrew Sullivan sparks ire of gay community over defense of former Mozilla CEO Brendan Eich|work=Tech Times|accessdate=2017-11-04|archive-date=2017-08-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170822151034/http://www.techtimes.com/articles/5432/20140412/andrew-sullivan-sparks-ire-of-gay-community-over-defense-of-former-mozilla-ceo-brendan-eich.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2015年5月28日，艾克成立Brave軟體公司，這是一家網際網路安全公司，已經從[[天使投資者|天使投資者]]募集了250萬美元的早期資金<ref name="cnet.com">{{cite web|url=http://www.cnet.com/au/news/mystery-startup-from-ex-mozilla-ceo-aims-to-go-where-tech-titans-wont/|title=Mystery startup from ex-Mozilla CEO aims to go where tech titans won't|date=17 November 2015|publisher=CBS Interactive|work=CNET|access-date=2017-11-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180615193112/https://www.cnet.com/au/news/mystery-startup-from-ex-mozilla-ceo-aims-to-go-where-tech-titans-wont/|archive-date=2018-06-15|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bizjournals.com/prnewswire/press_releases/2015/11/17/SF59778|title=Brave Software Raises $2.5 Million And Expands Technical Team|work=The Business Journals|accessdate=2017-11-04|archive-date=2017-11-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171129042209/https://www.bizjournals.com/prnewswire/press_releases/2015/11/17/SF59778|dead-url=no}}</ref>。該公司的聯合創始人Brian Bondy曾在Mozilla和[[可汗學院|可汗學院]]工作。2016年1月20日，該公司發布了[[Brave_(网页浏览器)|Brave網頁瀏覽器]]。2017年5月，Brave用30秒完成了约3千5百万美元的[[首次代币发行|ICO]]发售<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.coindesk.com/35-million-30-seconds-token-sale-internet-browser-brave-sells/|title=$35 Million in 30 Seconds: Token Sale for Internet Browser Brave Sells Out|accessdate=2017-06-01|date=May 31, 2017|publisher=CoinDest|archive-date=2017-06-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170601013605/http://www.coindesk.com/35-million-30-seconds-token-sale-internet-browser-brave-sells/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

